OL,3,CPolice Scotland appeal for information
OL,4,Cafter man dies in crash
OL,6,FA 75-year-old man has been confirmed
OL,7,Fdead following a car crash on the A7.
OL,9,FThe fatal crash happened near its
OL,10,Fjunction with Drove Road, north of
OL,11,FHawick just after 4.35pm on 12 January
OL,12,F2025.
OL,14,FThe driver of a black Suzuki Ignis - a
OL,15,F75-year-old man - was found dead at
OL,16,Fthe scene by emergency services.
