OL,3,CPolice Scotland appeal for information
OL,4,Cafter man dies in crash
OL,6,FA 52-year-old driver of a red Vauxhall
OL,7,FGrandland has been taken to Borders
OL,8,FGeneral Hospital. Medical staff
OL,9,Fdescribe her injuries as serious but
OL,10,Fstable.
OL,12,FPolice officers closed the road for
OL,13,Finvestigation work and reopened the
OL,14,Farea just after 12.15am on 13 January
OL,15,F2025.
OL,17,FPolice Scotland Sergeant Jamie Humpage
OL,18,Fsaid: "Our thoughts are with the
OL,19,Ffamily of the man who died.
