OL,3,CPolice Scotland appeal for information
OL,4,Cafter man dies in crash
OL,6,F"Enquiries are ongoing to establish
OL,7,Fthe full circumstances and we are keen
OL,8,Fto speak to anyone driving on the road
OL,9,Faround the time of the crash to get in
OL,10,Ftouch.
OL,12,F"I would also ask anyone driving on
OL,13,Fthis road between Selkirk and Hawick
OL,14,Faround the time of the crash with
OL,15,Fdashcam, to please check their footage
OL,16,Fand make contact with officers if it
OL,17,Fholds anything relevant."
